author: Emma Ockerman, Michael Learmonth
title: Michigan Governor: Go Ahead and Protest the Lockdown, But You Might Get Coronavirus and Die Alone
description: Michigan Democrat Gretchen Whitmer has had it with protests of her stay at home order at the state capitol.
content:
Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer has a message for the legion of protesters that swarmed Lansing Wednesday to protest her stay-at-home orders: Sure you can protest, but you might make someone you love sick and if they die of coronavirus they'll die alone.
